<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤١٩١ -<span class="c5"> مَالِك بَلَغَهُ:</span> أَنَّ عُمَرَ وَهَبَ لابْنِهِ جَارِيَةً،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> لا تَمَسَّهَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢٤⦘ فَإِنِّي قَدْ كَشَفْتُهَا <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
